structure.unit: AGRICULTURAL SEEDS, FEEDING STUFFS, AND FERTILIZERS

law.history: Repealed 1984 Ky. Acts ch. 191, sec. 21, effective July 13, 1984. -- Amended 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 125, sec. 6, effective June 19, 1952. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 1822-12.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Director to refuse registration if fertilizer thought worthless.
